{"tid":195221,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人割過雙眼皮","createTime":"2017-04-10T12:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T01:24:57.000Z","uid":23317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a019ff68d5d14e8eeb946a3540a0c809d550185","tid":195221,"uid":23317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"以前隻右眼做過手術<br />\n做完之後右眼個眼皮鬆哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雙眼皮變左內雙 隻眼細左成倍<br />\n<br />\n想問咁既情況割雙眼皮有冇幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋邊到做好 有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830cc58a6065d98eeedab017e12664aa704643d2","tid":195221,"uid":414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"呢啲都係去醫生個到會最適合<br />\n應該仲有咩拉提/抽脂<br />\n就算整雙眼皮都有好多種整法<br />\n你去多幾間到consult下"},{"pid":"f2160394c214c865bf3c73627487523e57925995","tid":195221,"uid":414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:18:09.000Z","msg":"見到好多人去台灣整<br />\n因為技術比香港成熟，又比韓國容易溝通"},{"pid":"e7d2b069580f3951d89529b734a1b4d037ad4b3e","tid":195221,"uid":76652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:47:22.000Z","msg":"整容撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2febf9b113875eea1106f11414c9f74217497d0f","tid":195221,"uid":23317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到好多人去台灣整<br />\n因為技術比香港成熟，又比韓國容易溝通</blockquote><br />\n台灣整係咪多數都平啲?"}]}